                    The overload of coronavirus content in the news recently has had a negative impact on mental health (i.e anxiety, isolation, problems sleeping, etc.).#[br]#[br]

                .media-container
                    img(src="../img/novid2.png", alt="search for a duck and view all current listings page")
                p.description.
                    Our team used a News API and scrubbed the data to redact and replace virus related words to establish a less-depressing place to read the most recent headlines.#[br]#[br]

                    The seal of approval was then given to all redacted articles and users have the option to redact extra words in the browser.
